Consider the following pseudo-code (all data items are of type integer):

procedure P(a, b, c);
    a := 2;
    c := a + b;
end {P}

begin
    x := 1;
    y := 5;
    z := 100;
    P(x, x*y, z);
    Write ('x = ', x, 'z = ', z);
end.

Determine its output, if the parameters are passed to the Procedure P by:
i. value
ii. reference
iii. name
